overview: Whether you like it or not, if you’re going to get ahead in business, you should get used to SERVICING THE CEO—just like the Lucas Men have in GENTLEMEN 29! Tomas Brand and Gustavo Cruz waste no time stripping off their suits. Nick Capra, Stas Landon, Andrey Vic, and Ben Batemen take a late-night meeting too far. Valentin Amour works long and hard to impress Sir Peter. And Kaden Alexander uses his authority to fuck Alexander Volkov into submission.
title: Gentlemen 29: Servicing The CEO
